videos.headline: Syracuse blocks FG to set up TD
videos.description: Syracuse blocks a 50-yard field goal and returns it for 31 yards, leading to a touchdown three plays later.

videos.headline: Louisville QB escapes pressure to fire TD
videos.description: QB Jawon Pass escapes the pocket pressure to sling a 13-yard touchdown to Dez Fitzpatrick, trimming Louisville's deficit to 10-7.

videos.headline: Syracuse RB finds daylight for 67-yard TD
videos.description: Moe Neal breaks through the middle for a 67-yard touchdown, putting Syracuse up 17-7.

videos.headline: Louisville QB picked off on 1st career college pass
videos.description: Louisville's backup QB gets hit while throwing on his first career collegiate pass attempt and gets picked off.

videos.headline: Syracuse keeps piling on with 65-yard TD
videos.description: Syracuse goes up 51-14 on a 65-yard touchdown from Eric Dungey to Nykeim Johnson.
